reviews.review_text: ok now... ...just concentrating on Feel Like A Stranger, being how strange I am...just tight and awesome and long too! They really had it down in 1980!

alright then... good show. The interplay between Brent and Jerry and the hole band for that matter on Stranger are worth listening too. as well as others in this era {west high auditorium}.Jerry is all around awesome on the guitar this night.pretty good sound. nice version of He's Gone.

Pretty hot show all around Some great jamming and you got to love the big, meaty tone from JG, who is very engaged the entire show. Nice interplay between the band, and because of the excellent mix and great sound quality of the recording, you can hear it all very clearly throughout.
